Package: predictlm
Title: reticulated PredictLM, a tabular foundation model from Zero One Research
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("frank", "hull", , "frankiethull@proton.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: provides R bindings to PredictLM, base and mini checkpoints. Base is a 26.2M-parameter transformer-based tabular foundation model that uses in-context learning to solve regression and classification in a single forward pass. mini is designed for edge devices.
